    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Offers unique gameplay mechanic by combining TCG and board game elements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Numerous cards, broadly classified into units, skills, and items.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player builds a “book” consisting of 50 cards, and then creates a strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Luck also plays a part in winning or losing, such as moves or card draws based on the roll of the dice.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can easily compete with your friends and rivals.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Video/Live Streaming  Guidelines</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Any individual or corporation can post videos and live-stream without prior permission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no restrictions on monetization or scope of play.</p>",
